    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and stir with a wooden spoon for 1 min</p><p>Gradually whisk in the<strong> stock</strong>, a little at a time, and cook for 5 min or until a thick sauce remains</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for later!) and stir through until melted – this is your <strong>white sauce</strong></p>",
